[SN]TITLE[SN]
County Down: School Reporters react to rise in homelessness

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
With homelessness on the rise in Northern Ireland, a group of pupils from Abbey Grammar School in Newry in County Down decided to take action to make a positive impact on their community.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
15 March 2017 Last updated at 22:08 GMT
